Institute of Legal Practice and Development yemewe na Minisiteri y’Uburezi mu rwanda, ni ikigo cyisumbuye cya leta giherereye mumujyi muto wa Nyanza (abaturage 250.499,999), Intara y'Amajyepfo. <ref>https://free-apply.com/en/university/1064600005</ref>

Institute of Legal Practice and Development (ILPD) ni ikigo cy’amategeko n’iterambere cyashyizweho n’Itegeko No 65/2013 ryo kuwa 27/08/3013. <ref>https://ilpd.ac.rw/index.php?id=2</ref>ILPD itanga amasomo na gahunda biganisha ku mpamyabumenyi y'amashuri makuru yemewe mu bice byinshi by’inyigisho.Iri shuri kandi ryahawe inshingano zo gutanga ubumenyi bw’umwuga ku bantu bafite nibura impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu by'amategeko, batanga amahugurwa ku bakora mu rwego rw'ubutabera no mu nzego zijyanye nabyo, guteza imbere ubushakashatsi no gukwirakwiza amategeko, gufatanya n'ibindi bigo by’ubushakashatsi no gukora ubushakashatsi mu Rwanda no mu mahanga, kandi bagashyigikira ikindi gikorwa icyo ari cyo cyose cyagira uruhare mu guteza imbere amategeko n'ubutabera.<ref>https://www.landportal.org/organization/institute-legal-practice-and-development-rwanda</ref>
